PrecisRegulations Amending the HUMANITARIAN DESIGNATED CLASSES REGULATIONS which set back the date on which these Regulations expire to December 31, 1999, and remove Cambodia from the list of countries (Source Country Class) whose citizens may, from within their own country, apply to enter Canada on humanitarian grounds, as of January 1, 1999.
